Package: duckbotos-lm-studio
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: wget, curl, gnupg2, apt-transport-https,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: LM Studio as first-class local model provider for DuckBotOS
 Installs LM Studio (https://lmstudio.ai) as a first-class provider in
 DuckBotOS. LM Studio provides local LLM inference with GPU acceleration
 (CUDA for NVIDIA, Metal for Apple Silicon, Vulkan cross-platform).
 .
 This package:
 - Adds the LM Studio official APT repository
 - Installs lm-studio package (headless CLI + API server)
 - Installs the LM Studio GUI for desktop use (optional, for kiosk mode)
 - Configures lm-studio API on port 1234 (localhost only)
 .
 LM Studio is the primary local model provider in DuckBotOS. Users can:
 - Connect via URL input in the DuckBotOS UI
 - Browse and download models from the LM Studio community model hub
 - Load GGUF models from local storage
 - Switch between local (GPU) and cloud providers seamlessly
 .
 Version: Latest stable from lmstudio.ai
Homepage: https://lmstudio.ai